2. Interpretation
In this Act, unless inconsistent with the context—
"Chairperson" means the Chairperson of the Ntlo ya Dikgosi , and includes any other Member when such other Member is presiding at a meeting of the Ntlo ya Dikgosi ;
"Member" means any Member of the Ntlo ya Dikgosi ;
"Ntlo ya Dikgosi " means the Ntlo ya Dikgosi established by section 77(1) of the Constitution;
[ 11 of 2005, s. 3. ]
"officer of the Ntlo ya Dikgosi " means the Secretary or any other person acting as an officer of the Ntlo ya Dikgosi under the orders of the Chairperson within the precincts of the Ntlo ya Dikgosi , and includes any member of the Botswana Police Force on duty within the precincts of the Ntlo ya Dikgosi ;
